title: WEEKNIGHT BEEF SKILLET RECIPE
directions: Cook noodles according to package directions.

Meanwhile, in a large nonstick skillet over medium heat, cook beef and pepper until meat is no longer pink; drain. Stir in mixed vegetables, tomato sauce, Worcestershire sauce, Italian seasoning, sugar and salt; heat through. Drain noodles; serve with meat mixture. Sprinkle with parsley. Yield: 4 servings.
ingredients: 3 cups uncooked yolk-free whole wheat noodles
1 package (16 ounces) frozen mixed vegetables, thawed and drained
